)"}, {"format_id": "dash-1427888038922319v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1596.641, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQOBKpty4_-GQrfWHTnoFeStFzDmK9S4KMUU9PqPYqGN0potPS9-7QwoH72BB-1XwLBwTCDhUnkfropBDP5Kd3zUDh5LZKbkpNmDunA.mp4?_nc_cat=102&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=huubIj7TiogQ7kNvwGOwmE5&&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=mOMp-qdpfnGn7DKQnBsuCQ&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af2Jt5ZuAk8fOOM-ZQF0CfuE3Klrd084uqQzBdpp6QDwaA&oe=69D79AD7", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 7956660, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/93.0.4577.15 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1596.641, "format": "dash-1427888038922319v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by joshuaspoetry", "description": "Does all pain have meaning?", "duration": 39.867, "timestamp": 1767918382, "uploader_id": "65324209519", "uploader": "Joshua De Schutter", "channel": "joshuaspoetry", "like_count": 27684, "comment_count": 579, "comments": [{"author": "charlem89", "author_id": "32219096", "id": "18117445027644501", "text": "I need a collection of his poems in book form.", "timestamp": 1775332566}, {"author": "j.nelmes15", "author_id": "4206446215", "id": "18108188689858275", "text": "So show me wat that hurt was for, did it make me stronger then before? Did I try my best? Did I past all the rest?. Tell me tell me so I can be. Did it mean anything? Was it worth the dampening? The stomping of my soul. But it made u stronger no? Yes but I don't wanna feel this feeling, like life is reeling. I travel near and far to find who I am and who you are. then y do u fear urself like a stranger from afar? I show u the way, even wen u say nay. These r lessons to be learned, memories to be yearned. Stop questioning me and the emotions I put in u and the feelings I instill in u, I am with u, look around I can fill u, with the joy and happiness, without any mess, but without the pain, wat is there to gain?... ❤️", "timestamp": 1775274128}, {"author": "iandoloaaron", "author_id": "79767671306", "id": "18104379124902296", "text": "Jeremiah 29:11-12“‘For I well know the thoughts that I am thinking toward you,’ declares Jehovah, ‘thoughts of peace, and not of calamity, to give you a future and a hope.  12 And you will call me and come and pray to me, and I will listen to you.", "timestamp": 1775199087}, {"author": "iandoloaaron", "author_id": "79767671306", "id": "17922173322294604", "text": "I see you brother. Your life has more meaning than your aware of yet. I can tell from your expressions in all your videos that you think \"heavily\". Thats a weight i understand. You dont just have a purpose, but also a responsibility. And that my friend is the gift of God. An adventure we get to journey through the rarest of experiences called life. We get to eak out a lifetime of joy at the cost of a lifetime of pain.", "timestamp": 1775199051}, {"author": "lileileenandbofus", "author_id": "40759725599", "id": "17876010843436457", "text": "❤️❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1775096255}, {"author": "liz.ker.9", "author_id": "47720309511", "id": "17941832244174165", "text": "You are talent beyond talent👏👏👏", "timestamp": 1774906234}, {"author": "misschadbourne", "author_id": "6694579130", "id": "18111701410703708", "text": "It doesn’t mean anything til u make it mean something", "timestamp": 1774876011}, {"author": "demented_damsel_in_a_dress", "author_id": "10581247959", "id": "18117912673628939", "text": "Thank you !", "timestamp": 1774831771}, {"author": "thatpennerguy", "author_id": "4106622695", "id": "18058942280650816", "text": "I feel this now, deep down.  I’ve live with bipolar disorder for 17 years.  2 hospitalizations, multiple mental breakdowns, 1 fractured skull and half a body paralyzed later, and it’s only getting harder to deal with.  On top of that, 6 months ago I started developing a lung issue that looks like it could be COPD.  I’m only 36.  Why?  For what?", "timestamp": 1774763285}, {"author": "shanagafitness", "author_id": "6963848691", "id": "18096878903044299", "text": "Life throws that lemon to me that doesn't make lemonade a few time and it hurts", "timestamp": 1774759782}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/612064080_1183027427368471_3918099602493777532_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH1KM9Fc5Ztc1jLKkm-1HpVNAHzgZOlXnvdgCk4UfLQj9kx3zv4XRjbyBiNS0BvfmY&_nc_ohc=13cLJnRHAqgQ7kNvwEVL41U&_nc_gid=mOMp-qdpfnGn7DKQnBsuCQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2Vcwwsvc7iTcgucjtjuccg-XMS7QzSz-vLjOPNPP8JtQ&oe=69D78A45&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/612064080_1183027427368471_3918099602493777532_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH1KM9Fc5Ztc1jLKkm-1HpVNAHzgZOlXnvdgCk4UfLQj9kx3zv4XRjbyBiNS0BvfmY&_nc_ohc=13cLJnRHAqgQ7kNvwEVL41U&_nc_gid=mOMp-qdpfnGn7DKQnBsuCQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2Vcwwsvc7iTcgucjtjuccg-XMS7QzSz-vLjOPNPP8JtQ&oe=69D78A45&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/